{"tid":294433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉] 這就是中國人的教育水平！","createTime":"2017-06-23T03:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T14:25:54.000Z","uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b174a0f24fe8b9dbb4438ee395c9fe3cc2d56b","tid":294433,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/23/110613_bd7166424dd82d817791be3b1664123d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F23%2F110613_bd7166424dd82d817791be3b1664123d.png&h=05ba914f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在日本的埼玉縣川口市中，有一處名為「川口芝園團地」的公共屋邨。幾年前不斷有中國人入住，現在中國居民比率已佔整體的三分之二。<br />\n<br />\n結果，在屋邨附近的公園每天都滿地垃圾，中國人還四處大小異便，吐痰。而且他們並不是會把垃圾妥善處理的民族，只會隨地扔下。在家中製造的垃圾則從家中扔到街上當作處理。因此屋邨附近的道路已經不能安心地行走，要隨時提防頭上會有垃圾從天而降。<br />\n<br />\n總括而言，中國人不懂正確地處理垃圾。所以中國的居民愈是增加，街道便愈變荒廢，不衛生。真是個難應付的民族。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19397051_1957017131211444_1672371953999455090_n.jpg?oh=1484f109aa99a1095d37a07c466d6c1f&amp;oe=59C54E42\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19397051_1957017131211444_1672371953999455090_n.jpg%3Foh%3D1484f109aa99a1095d37a07c466d6c1f%26oe%3D59C54E42&h=3a2b01d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19225993_1957017381211419_6032095080907662057_n.jpg?oh=63206878eea6de7e0d00452934b882de&amp;oe=59D5E60C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19225993_1957017381211419_6032095080907662057_n.jpg%3Foh%3D63206878eea6de7e0d00452934b882de%26oe%3D59D5E60C&h=651f1566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/19250860_1957017634544727_5645335229189241748_o.jpg?oh=89e6f872f7fd3d7a236cfa20a9478576&amp;oe=59DD54FF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F19250860_1957017634544727_5645335229189241748_o.jpg%3Foh%3D89e6f872f7fd3d7a236cfa20a9478576%26oe%3D59DD54FF&h=0cdae7f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"525bbe6942b9bae3b897cd450b1a1496a8113a08","tid":294433,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"中國人：这只是個別例子，不要丟我們中国人的架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34176003f0e7172385ef96ab4d93ad0aefa4e6b8","tid":294433,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"一拳超人個縣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1569eb75e88fe021df8b06b59a8ae213f17ecc1f","tid":294433,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:11:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一拳超人個縣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n神級災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75386a3ac7a61aad7602a8178709e8d5e3d4b86","tid":294433,"uid":57513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"無支那狗入黎堆"},{"pid":"c9f1bd9bc61a61de9ccfd85aed29e287c27a01cf","tid":294433,"uid":120859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:32:12.000Z","msg":"其實話佢哋冇公德心係冇用<br />\n佢哋反而會覺得自己好醒"},{"pid":"074b7f93313fe0bcbd267d4d61bfbdb90d440b3c","tid":294433,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:35:31.000Z","msg":"點解佢地會係日本長期居留到?"},{"pid":"4e71258deb51f5fcaa7022ad2fe89c8c33a1f154","tid":294433,"uid":22529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:37:39.000Z","msg":"污染地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c809df9786e311116732fc1c1ca70d3adaad5227","tid":294433,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實話佢哋冇公德心係冇用<br />\n佢哋反而會覺得自己好醒</b